
Using .gitignore
eg: add the following:
.vscode/
notes/
*.java  # will ignore files with extension .java

------------------

Global Ignore File

	git config --global core.excludesfile [file]

------------------
Clearing the Cache:
	git rm -r --cached .(current directory)

	--> after a lot of commits, there migth be a number cached stuffs makeing it messy, we clear that using the above command.


